item.title: How do i make portals
item.dc:creator: @WRX WRX`
item.description:
@WRX wrote:

Create a method (Void) with those inside, and place it inside packet 121.

Here…

First, add this void underneath another.

public void spawnportals() {
makeGlobalObject(3360, 3263, 4150, 0, 10);//portal
               makeGlobalObject(3360, 3264, 4151, 0, 10);//portal
               makeGlobalObject(3360, 3265, 4152, 0, 10);//portal
               makeGlobalObject(3360, 3266, 4153, 0, 10);//portal
               makeGlobalObject(3374, 3266, 4154, 0, 10);//portal
               makeGlobalObject(3374, 3265, 4155, 0, 10);//portal
               makeGlobalObject(3374, 3264, 4156, 0, 10);//portal
               makeGlobalObject(3364, 3270, 4157, 0, 10);//portal
               makeGlobalObject(3361, 3270, 2465, 0, 10);//portal
               makeGlobalObject(3373, 3270, 2474, 0, 10);//portal
}

Now, search packet 121.

case 121:

Add the following inside the packet:

spawnportals();
